      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a strong claim. To be honest, we've had issues with other brands claiming \"all-day\" life only to have them die halfway through a heavy load. Do you have any specific test data or documentation from your engineering team that verifies the 24-hour mark under continuous, high-torque operation? I need to see something before I can sign off on this.",
